# SCALE asset pages: dynamic prospect slugs from R2 — rewrite all
# /asset/* requests to the single shell page built by Next.js static export.
# Next.js with default trailingSlash:false emits /asset/__shell__.html (a flat
# file), NOT /asset/__shell__/index.html, so the rewrite target must be the
# .html file. The client reads the real slug from window.location.pathname.
/asset/* /asset/__shell__.html 200
